# Secrets and credentials — never commit. `grit config set-azure/set-s3` writes
# access keys into .grit/config.json (already covered by the .grit rule above);
# these patterns guard against stray credential files landing in the repo.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.pfx
*.p12
*credentials*
*secret*.json
.aws/
.azure/
